welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Oberschleissheim, a charming city known for its rich history and picturesque surroundings. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer: from its beautiful palaces to its quaint local shops and restaurants. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 2

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, with unlimited access and no time limit.
